{
  "stem": "25773.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was very clean, even in these circumstances with other people who we lived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other people had also to move out, so it was only I with my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I actually wish that he should die because it was, it was-- we knew that somehow, somehow or other there is something not quite right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he-- I saved him because I cleaned the clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what was the saver?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he was starved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In typhoid if you don't eat, then you survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And shortly afterwards, we were called that we have to go to the Tobbens Schultz premises.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was the-- at my-- at the time, just at this time, I managed my brother to, to, to, to, to get him to the big ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went-- and actually if I may tell you that I went myself with him there and crossed the no man's land, which was very dangerous because already at the time the Germans begin to select people for selection and took them at random straight to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know yet that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I managed to take him to this place, to this shop where he was with the electric workshop.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to the place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I found the place with my grandmother-- my grandfather was not alive anymore-- and my auntie, and her son, and her husband used to live.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a beautiful flat, big flat with, with, with, with a balcony and flowers on it, and-- in Nowolipki Street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was also extraordinary experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I found the place, but was a complete-- I forgot to tell you that the-- already in '41, they have, the Germans began the selection.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Slowly, but they began the-- not slowly, rather, rather quite consistently.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
